column5: You’re a good person, thank you for reporting it.
No matter what I do there’s no bugs :(
Hey. You are not alone, I’m here for you man. You don’t know me and I don’t know but you can always come talk to me.
Hey man. Merry Christmas! I’m sorry your family is so lame. Please know you are not alone, message me if you need anyone to talk to!
Omg why did you give in?
Of course! Here or direct message, whatever you like :)

Hey. I know exactly how you’re feeling right now. I’m not here to tell you what you should and shouldn’t do, but I am here to tell you that you are not alone. We probably live far away from eachother but I am always here if you need or want someone to talk to. I know how much it sucks to feel like you’re alone and you have no one. You have me.

It’s okay haha! I just keep causing these issues, like I keep doing things wrong and upsetting people. I feel like a burden even tho I know I’m loved.  Every time I feel like “oh things are better” something happens and I immediately consider suicide. It’s starting to scare me, like part of me doesn’t want to die because I’m scared of death. But living sometimes gets so hard, does that make sense?
I care about you. I really do. And I’m here for you
Hi, thanks for responding. SO means significant other
